@york-yu-ctw : Can you raise a support ticket against redshift? looks like hudi::ParsedFilename::IsValidCommitTimestamp has to be fixed when using 0.10.0. 
unfortunately, we did not guard the change behind a config. we have to fix it forward. We tested the ms change with spark, hive, presto and trino. but could not test against all engines/envs. 

CCn @umehrot2. Is there any quick work around you can think of to tackle this?

@BenjMaq : Is timeline server running? 
Just to unblock you: Can you try disabling timeline server explicitly and giving it a try in the mean time ethan assists us here. 
hoodie.embed.timeline.server=false.

